<br>
The bottom line is -<br>
<br>
Draughts are resisted less, and are small nukes.<br>
<br>
Strike of Solusek is higher DPS, and a HUGE nuke.<br>
<br>
It is easier to cast Strike of Solusek &quot;too early&quot; and take aggro if the MT has unreliable aggro management or you have bad luck/poor timing.  If you cast Strike of Solusek &quot;too late&quot;, I.E. just before a mob is killed, you are likely to lose efficiency by dealing only a fraction of the spell's damage to the target, virtually &quot;nuking the corpse&quot;.<br>
<br>
Draughts are simply easier to manage, and more reliable.  However, if you have Quick Damage 3, or aggro and resists are not a concern at all, Strike of Solusek is clearly superior.<br>
<br>
I have Agnarr's Thunder currently, and I can't WAIT to get Strike of Solusek...but there is no way I will be using it exclusively.  In all likelihood, I will open up on a mob like I do now (with Xuzl!) with a draught, Mana Robe click or Concussion, and then the larger nuke.  I have Quick Damage 3 and Spell Casting Subtlety 3, so the ability to deliver a large amount of damage quickly is valuable to me since I can use the time saved regenerating mana by clicking my Mana Robe.  I wish I had clicky Concussion pants!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elyia>Elyia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 253<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/5/03 8:57:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26371.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.keepersofthefaith.org/images/KTF_medium.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: aggro decay</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Strike of Solusek is higher DPS, and a HUGE nuke.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
